==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Scorification
<hw>Sco`ri*fi*ca"tion</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Cf. F.
<ets>scorification</ets>. See <er>Scorify</er>.]</ety>
<fld>(Chem.)</fld> <def>The act, process, or result of scorifying, or
reducing to a slag; hence, the separation from earthy matter by means of
a slag; <as>as, the <ex>scorification</ex> of ores</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Scorifier</ent>⟦br⟧
